These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, potato, grapefruit, corn
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep, indie, electronic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daisy, begonia, iris
House: cottage, cape-cod, victorian, farmhouse
 1. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person who growsdahlia##8
 2. the cottage house is not to the left of the cottage house##8
 3. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growsdahlia is not to the left of the person who growsiris##8
 5. the cottage house is not to the right of the cottage house##8
 6. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 7. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
 8. the fan of electronic is between the cape-cod house and the person who growsdaisy##2
 9. the farmhouse house is the fan of indie##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person eating corn##1
11. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
12. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
13. the fan of indie is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
14. the person eating potato is the victorian house##1
15. the person eating potato is not the person who growsdaisy##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Food         | cabbage     | potato   | corn | grapefruit |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | electronic   | gospel   | indie  |
| Flower         | daisy  | begonia  | iris  | dahlia |
| House     | cottage    | victorian | cape-cod     | farmhouse    |

