.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, lawyer, coach, videographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, water-polo, tennis, cricket
House: futuristic, art-deco, modern, victorian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, fonseca, pall-mall, aristoff
 1. the modern house is between the bongani-smoker and the art-deco house##2
 2. the lawyer is not to the right of the fonseca-smoker##8
 3. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 4. the software-developer is not to the right of the aristoff-smoker##8
 5. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
 6. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the videographer##8
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the aristoff-smoker##5
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the futuristic house is the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the modern house is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
11. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the modern house##8
12. the videographer is on the left of the lawyer##1
13. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
14. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the modern house##3
15. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
17. the software-developer is not to the right of the art-deco house##8
18. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the fonseca-smoker##8
19. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Job      | software-developer | coach | videographer  | lawyer  |
| Sport          | cricket     | water-polo | swimming | tennis  |
| House   | art-deco    | modern  | victorian | futuristic |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | aristoff | bongani    | fonseca  |

