.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, mirinda, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, teacher, chef, musician
House: cape-cod, craftsman, colonial, futuristic
4 different games are played: domino, billiard, mah-jongg, whist
 1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the musician##5
 4. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the analyst##8
 6. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the chef##8
 7. the colonial house is in an odd position##4
 8. the chef is on the left of the musician##1
 9. the musician is on the left of the teacher##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
11. the analyst is not to the left of the craftsman house##8
12. the musician is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | almond-milk    | fanta   | mirinda | juice |
| Job   | analyst     | chef  | musician   | teacher      |
| House   | craftsman | cape-cod    | colonial      | futuristic       |
| Game         | mah-jongg    | domino | whist   | billiard    |

