.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, iris, daffodil
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, snake, hamster
City: nizza, boston, colone, london
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, russian, german, nigerian
 1. the owner of the snake is not the person traveling to nizza##6
 2. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the german##3
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to boston##2
 5. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the italian##3
 6. the italian is not to the right of the person who growsaconite##8
 7. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
10. the person traveling to boston is the italian##1
11. the russian is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
12. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the russian##3
13. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
14. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the russian##3
15. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Flower    | iris    | aconite             | sunflower   | daffodil     |
| Pet   | cat | snake            | hamster | ferret    |
| City     | boston | london | nizza  | colone |
| Nationality   | italian  | russian               | german  | nigerian   |

