.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-5::.
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, whist, domino
House: art-deco, palace, victorian, craftsman
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, rock, metal, house
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
 1. the art-deco house is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 2. the fan of house is the person playing snooker##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person playing chess##6
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the victorian house##1
 5. the art-deco house is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the art-deco house##8
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person playing snooker##8
 8. the fan of rock is the palace house##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is not to the left of the person playing domino##8
10. the victorian house is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person playing domino and the palace house##2
12. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of rock is not to the right of the palace house##8
14. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the palace house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Game         | domino     | chess | whist   | snooker  |
| House   | craftsman | art-deco   | palace     | victorian  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | metal     | rock | house  |
| Beverage         | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate | milk   | iced-tea |

