 2. the wooden house is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8
 3. the wooden house is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 4. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
 5. the cape-cod house is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##8
 7. the person watching disaster movies is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the cape-cod house and the person watching disaster movies##7
 9. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
13. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
14. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
15. the wooden house is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
