.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, strawberry, pepper
4 different games are played: billiard, whist, mah-jongg, bridge
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, skateboard, scooter, van
City: venice, liverpool, hannover, berlin
 1. the person traveling to berlin is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 2. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 3. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
 4. the person driving the ship is not the person playing whist##6
 5. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 8. the person eating pepper is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person eating cabbage and the person playing bridge##7
10. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
11. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
12. the person traveling to berlin is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
13. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
14. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
15. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |    4     |
| Food      | corn  | pepper      | cabbage    | strawberry |
| Game   | bridge    | mah-jongg   | billiard    | whist  |
| Transport   | scooter | ship    | skateboard | van  |
| City           | berlin     | liverpool | hannover | venice     |

