 3. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
 6. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the person eating cranberry and the person eating garlic##7
 7. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
 8. the craftsman house is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsaconite##7
 9. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
11. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
13. the cape-cod house is the person who growsbegonia##1
14. the person who growsbegonia is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8
15. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
