14. the person who likes pink is not to the right of the person who likes purple##8
15. the person who likes pink is the person eating strawberry##1
16. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person eating zucchini##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Color           | white | pink       | emerald      | purple  |
| Food   | pear    | strawberry | zucchini   | asparagus   |
| Cigar   | montecristo   | swisher          | cain      | davidoff  |
| Birthday   | july   | september      | january | june |

